Hello,
I would like to request support for this Tuya Zigbee wall switch:

ModelId: TS0011

ManufacturerName: _TZ3000_hafsqare

Type: 1‑gang wall switch (one physical relay)

Added as: Unknown Zigbee Device in Homey Pro 2023

Below is the full Zigbee interview.

Important notes about this device:
This TS0011 unit is mains‑powered (230V), even though it incorrectly reports:

powerSource: "battery"

deviceType: "enddevice"

receiveWhenIdle: false

Because of this incorrect reporting, Homey treats it as a sleepy device, even though it is always powered and should behave as a router.

This behavior is common in several Tuya TS0011/TS0012/TS0013 variants.

The device controls one real load and works correctly, but the Zigbee metadata is misleading.

